NYMEX to lower natgas futures spread margins Mon . The New York Mercantile Exchange ( NYMEX ) said Monday it will decrease margins on spreads involving second month Henry Hub natural gas futures as of the close of business today . The rates will be lowered to $ 500 from $ 3 , 800 for clearing members ; to $ 550 from $ 4 , 180 for customers ; and to $ 675 from $ 5 , 130 for customers , NYMEX said in a statement . ( ( - - New York Power Desk 212 - 859 - 1624 ) ) 
